Package core.data.machine

Class AMachineData

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.data.AData
      • core.data.machine.AMachineData
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ADeviceData, ServerData
    public abstract class AMachineData
extends AData
    Abstract class for something representing a "Machine" on our network. A machine, at its most basic, is something with network interfaces. This means it can also talk TCP and UDP, can be throttled, and has a name somewhere in DNS-world. Any of the properties of a "Machine" may be null, this is not where we're doing error checking! :)
